{"id":2762,"date":"2016-02-26T13:58:39","date_gmt":"2016-02-26T13:58:39","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/?p=2762"},"modified":"2016-03-10T11:12:59","modified_gmt":"2016-03-10T11:12:59","slug":"launching-makerassemblyni-16th-march","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/2016\/02\/launching-makerassemblyni-16th-march\/","title":{"rendered":"Launching @MakerAssemblyNI: 16th March"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><strong>EDIT: Schedule released below<\/strong><br \/>\nWe&#8217;ve been quietly toiling away in the background to bring the movers, shakers and taste makers of the UK Maker Community \u00a0(and beyond!) to Belfast for a one day mini-conference, set up to tear down some misconceptions about the community and to address some of the unique challenges faced in our region.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/makerassemblyni.org\">Maker Assembly NI<\/a> is a one-day gathering hosted in the labs to critically discuss maker culture: its meaning, politics, history and future.<\/p>\n<h2>Speakers<\/h2>\n<p>Currently confirmed speakers \/ workshop leaders are:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/javiburon\">Javier Buron<\/a> from <a href=\"http:\/\/Colaborativa.eu\" target=\"_blank\">Colaborativa.eu<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/norette\" target=\"_blank\">Nora O&#8217;Murchu<\/a> from the <a href=\"http:\/\/www.idc.ul.ie\/people\/nora-o-murchu\" target=\"_blank\">University of Limerick Interaction Design Centre<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/codekat\" target=\"_blank\">Kat Braybrooke<\/a> from the\u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/www.sussex.ac.uk\/shl\/\" target=\"_blank\">University of Sussex Humanities Lab<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/freerange_inc\" target=\"_blank\">Hannah Stewart<\/a>\u00a0from\u00a0the <a href=\"http:\/\/futuremakespaces.rca.ac.uk\/\" target=\"_blank\">RCA Future Makerspaces project<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.fablabs.io\/users\/1098\">Adam Wallace<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.fablabs.io\/users\/641\">Nim Durey<\/a>, from <a href=\"http:\/\/www.fablabni.com\/\" target=\"_blank\">FabLabNI<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/JohnPeto\">John Peto<\/a>\u00a0from <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/Nerve_Centre\">Nerve Centre<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id='gallery-1' class='gallery galleryid-2762 gallery-columns-3 gallery-size-medium'><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/0.jpg'><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/0-300x225.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-2776\" srcset=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/0-300x225.jpg 300w, \/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/0-1024x768.jpg 1024w, \/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/0.jpg 1199w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/a>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<figcaption class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-2776'>\n\t\t\t\tJavier Buron from Colaborativa.eu\n\t\t\t\t<\/figcaption><\/figure><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/norette.jpg'><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/norette-300x200.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-2763\" srcset=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/norette-300x200.jpg 300w, \/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/norette.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/a>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<figcaption class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-2763'>\n\t\t\t\tNora O\u2019Murchu from the University of Limerick Interaction Design Centre\n\t\t\t\t<\/figcaption><\/figure><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/4909232307_71bd63bc4f.j